Method Detail

improve

public Quality improve(Node[] giantTour,
                       Quality bestResult)
Description copied from class: XFVRPOptImpBase
This abstract method is implemented by the explicit neighborhood generating operators like 2-opt or 3-opt. The giantTour will be changed by the improve method, where as the bestResult won't be changed. The resulting quality represents the fitness of the changed and imrpoved giantTour. If the result is null, no improvement was found and giant tour was not changed.
